{"tid":1393048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法政匯思：倘檢控涉政治考慮則破壞法治","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T05:45:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6152cc5e159f3db5aa30a467cf6985114aea1f29","tid":1393048,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"律政司檢控人員發公開信，點名批評律政司司長鄭若驊其身不正，處理牽涉大型公眾活動的案件時主要考慮政治因素，視檢控原則如糞土。<br />\n<br />\n法政匯思召集人李安然接受電台訪問表示，相關指控嚴重，如果屬實，鄭若驊是破壞法治，涉及政治考慮，令部分人更容易被控告，令法律面前人人平等這個法治核心元素崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n此外，節目上多名市民致電批評警方短短兩日即以暴動罪檢控檢控44人，質疑政府是破壞法治，不是保護法治。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n李安然指出，暴動罪是涉及在非法集結中，有人作出破壞社會安寧的行為，若有人在場，雖未協助暴力行為亦有機會涉及暴動罪。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2206307/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2206307%2F&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl52%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=0689b435\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2206307/</a>"},{"pid":"76217c260cb11330a17a2938ce8e8d945fce84d7","tid":1393048,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"咁要求不檢控係咪破壞法治？"},{"pid":"6125217f0b08cbd7666f2a9a47c0fa4bc8a88219","tid":1393048,"uid":118344,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"76217c260cb11330a17a2938ce8e8d945fce84d7","tid":1393048,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"咁要求不檢控係咪破壞法治？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"所以要求特赦"},{"pid":"4c5d431910230fab3368ac846509c9d5d3d35eef","tid":1393048,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f7225c61a192c7e6e577ed8a99f85b13ea5f69","tid":1393048,"uid":92448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"76217c260cb11330a17a2938ce8e8d945fce84d7","t